.Ar subspec
has the following format:
.Bd -unfilled -offset 3n
.Ar hash-table Ns Op , Ns Ar ...
.Ed
.Pp
.Ar hash-table
may be one of the following:
.Pp
.Bl -tag -compact -offset 3n -width 13n
