has the following format:
.Pp
.Bd -unfilled -offset 3n
.Ar iostats Ns Op , Ns Ar ...
.Ed
.Pp
.Ar iostats
may be one of the following:
.Pp
.Bl -tag -compact -offset 3n -width 3n
.It Cm lni-rcv- Ns Ar if ,
.It Cm lni-snd- Ns Ar if
